#NewSong2025 #NewHindiSong #RomanticSong #EmraanHashmi #YamiGautam #EmraanYami #HindiSong #HindiNewSong #NewRomanticSong #NewHindiSong2025 #EmraanHashmiNewSong #YamiGautamNewSong #RomanticSongHindi #HindiSong2025 #BetaabDil #SaritDutta

‚ÄúBetaab Dil‚Äù is a heart-touching romantic Hindi song that brings back the golden era of 90s Bollywood music. Sung and composed by Sarit Dutta, this soulful melody beautifully captures the emotions of love, longing, and separation. The heartfelt lyrics by Dr. Uma Naveen Mehta paint a timeless picture of a betaab (restless) heart waiting for its beloved.

If you miss the charm of classic love songs, ‚ÄúBetaab Dil‚Äù will take you straight back to that nostalgic era of melody and emotion.

üéß Experience ‚ÄúBetaab Dil‚Äù ‚Äî A Pure Hindi Romantic Love Song
Close your eyes, feel the rhythm, and let this song remind you of the beautiful simplicity of true love. Perfect for anyone who believes in eternal romance and misses the soulful tunes of the 90s

üëâ Don‚Äôt forget to LIKE, SHARE & SUBSCRIBE for more soulful music.

Subscribe : https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCWj7oD9SuDcGciiBQT9BQuw?sub_confirmation=1
__________________________________________________

Song Credits
Song : Betaab Dil
Singer : Sarit Dutta
Music Composer : Sarit Dutta
Lyrics : Dr Uma Naveen Mehta
Backing Vocals : Subhajit Das
Music Produced, Mixed & Mastered by Sarit Dutta @ Rivertone Studio
__________________________________________________

Lyrics:-

Hum chahe itna hi 
Ab tera saath ho
Kya tune kabhi ye jana
Kitna dard hai mujhko

Bekhudi mein chal pade hai
Khudko hi ab mitane
Mere kadam rukte nahi 
Teri galiyon me aane se

Deewangi ki had se jyada
Hum karte hai ye pyaar tumko
Ankhon mein teri yaadein wo leke
Betaab dil chahe tujhko

Baaton ne teri
Mujhko saari raat jagaya
Sanson ne teri
Mujhko yu apna banaya

Koi lamha nahi hai mera
Jisme tu nazar na aaya
Na hamne koi khata ki
fir kyu tune di hai saja

Deewangi ki had se jyada
Hum karte hai ye pyaar tumko
Ankhon mein teri yaadein wo leke
Betaab dil chahe tujhko

snippet.title: NZ vs WI | 1st T20I | Highlights | West Indies Tour Of New Zealand 2025
snippet.description:
West Indies defeated New Zealand by 7 runs in the first T20I at Eden Park in Auckland on November 5, 2025. New Zealand captain Mitchell Santner's half-century ultimately went in vain as the West Indies bowlers successfully defended their total. Matthew Forde was impressive with the ball early on, while Romario Shepherd held his nerve in the final over to secure the win for the West Indies.

snippet.title: Zindagi Imtihan Leti Hai (Lyric Video) | Amitabh Bachchan, Hema Malini | Naseeb
snippet.description:
Experience the depth and emotion of ‚ÄúZindagi Imtihan Leti Hai‚Äù ‚Äî the soulful classic from Bollywood‚Äôs legendary film Naseeb (1981).Sung by Kailash Kher, Anwar, and Suman Kalyanpur, this song beautifully captures life‚Äôs struggles, hope, and resilience through its heartfelt lyrics and timeless melody.Featuring stellar performances by Amitabh Bachchan, Shatrughan Sinha, and Hema Malini, this track remains one of the most inspiring and emotional gems of Hindi cinema.  

Credits: 
Singer: Dr.Kamlesh Avastathi, Anwar, Suman Kalyanpur
Music: Laxmikant-Pyarelal
Lyrics: Anand Bakshi
Movie: Naseeb
Starring: Amitabh Bachchan, Hema Malini
Director: Manmohan Desai
Producer: Manmohan Desai
Label: Universal Music India

Lyrics: 

 Zindagi Imtihaan Leti Hai, Zindagi Imtihaan Leti Hai 
 Logon Ki Jaan, Logon Ki Jaan, Logon Ki Jaan Leti Hai 
 Dillagi Imtihaan Leti Hai, Dillagi Imtihaan Leti Hai 
 Diljalon Ki Jaan, Diljalon Ki Jaan, Diljalon Ki Jaan Leti Hai 
 Dosti Imtihaan Leti Hai, Dosti Imtihaan Leti Hai 
 Doston Ki Jaan, Doston Ki Jaan, Doston Ki Jaan Leti Hai 
 Zindagi Imtihaan Leti Hai, Dillagi Imtihaan Leti Hai 
 Dosti Imtihaan Leti Hai 
  
 Us Bekhabar Ko Koi Khabar De, Us Bekhabar Ko Koi Khabar De 
 Ke Yeh Pyaar Hum Ko Paagal Naa Kar De 
 Yeh Pyaar Hum Ko Paagal Naa Kar De 
 Preet Bhi Imtihaan Leti Hai, Preet Bhi Imtihaan Leti Hai 
 Premiyon Ki Jaan, Premiyon Ki Jaan, Premiyon Ki Jaan Leti Hai 
 Zindagi Imtihaan Leti Hai, Zindagi Imtihaan Leti Hai 

Woh Paas Ho To Khul Na Sake Lab  

Woh Paas Ho To Khul Na Sake Lab 
  
Woh Door Ho To Sochein Mile Kab  

Woh Door Ho To Sochein Mile Kab 
  
Bebasi Imtihaan Leti Hai 

Bebasi Imtihaan Leti Hai 
  
Bebason Ki Jaan, Bebason Ki Jaan 
  
Bebason Ki Jaan Leti Hai 
  
Dillagi Imtihaan Leti Hai  

Dillagi Imtihaan Leti Hai 
  
 Dil Ki Gali Se Bach Ke Guzarna, Dil Ki Gali Se Bach Ke Guzarna 
 Yeh Soch Lena Phir Pyaar Karna, Yeh Soch Lena Phir Pyaar Karna 
 Aashiqi Imtihaan Leti Hai, Aashiqi Imtihaan Leti Hai 
 Aashiqon Ki Jaan, Aashiqon Ki Jaan, Aashiqon Ki Jaan Leti Hai 
 Dosti Imtihaan Leti Hai, Dosti Ki Jaan 
  
 Zindagi Imtihaan Leti Hai, Zindagi Imtihaan Leti Hai

I am a prisoner in this high security prison, the only way out is to dig a big hole by spoon, Can I find enough time and skills to do that? What if someone catches me? I have to use my connections in prison to plan my escape. It's time to dig a big big hole and find my way out!

Some of my funniest videos...Check it out!
Granny Remake ‚ñ∂ https://youtu.be/tsMq9he64ts
Will You Press the Button? ‚ñ∂ https://youtu.be/WCAuL1dOZks
Meeting Warden in Minecraft ‚ñ∂ https://youtu.be/tcWiS-cXEFg
Outlast Jumpscare Moments‚ñ∂ https://youtu.be/jjOsKtVf-kU
